# Google Apps Script web app webhook URL for contact + open-house form
# submissions. Becca creates a Google Sheet with tabs "Contact" + "Open House"
# and pastes templates/apps-script/Code.gs into Extensions > Apps Script, then
# deploys as a Web app (Execute as: Me / Who has access: Anyone). Copy the
# generated URL here for local dev, or set it in Vercel env vars for prod.
# When this is unset, form submissions return an error and the inline error
# state is shown to the user.
NEXT_PUBLIC_APPS_SCRIPT_WEBHOOK_URL=
